name: Freely
description:
We’re all longing to live our life freely. Respect each other eventhough we are destined to live in different places. Each night i dream about living side by side despite our race, ethnicity, culture, religion, or even different taste of art. I wish we can be more understand about the meaning of freedom for life.

Subject of the photo is the statue of West Irian liberation with Istiqlal Mosque and the cathedral church as the background.
This photo was taken in 2019, Jakarta.

4000 × 5579 px
